popescu2014time.title: Time corpora: Epochs, opinions and changes
popescu2014time.author: Popescu, Octavian and Strapparava, Carlo
popescu2014time.typeNotRelevantText: The expression "moral values" is analyzed in the paper as an expression occurring in Google n-grams (see section 4.1). The paper is about epoch delimitation and finding statistically significant changes in n-grams frequencies. This paper is not about analyzing morality/moral values.
